`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``
`8Keywords``   : Bank
`8Categories`` : 
`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``

`8Syntax:`` 

bank deposit <amount>:
	deposit some gold in your account 
bank withdraw <amount>:
	withdraw some gold from your account 
bank balance:
	check your balance 
bank transfer <amount> <victim>:
	transfer some gold to someone else 

 These commands are for managing your bank account and may only be done at a
banker. The most commonly used banker is Nathalie, who is located (from Recall)
2 south, 3 west, 2 north, 2 east and 1 south.

`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``
